🚀 Employee Growth Tracker – RAG vs Knowledge Graph System

A Comparison between Traditional RAG and a Knowledge Graph-based system for employee development insights.

This  allows users to ask questions about employee growth, skills, and performance using natural language.

Question Like :
“What skills are required for promotion?”
“How does employee performance impact career growth?”

🎯 Used 
🔹 Traditional RAG
Document chunking
Embeddings + FAISS
Retrieval-based answers from employee data

🔹 Knowledge Graph
Entity extraction (Employees, Skills, Performance, Promotions)

Neo4j relationships
Contextual reasoning across employee growth factors

📊 Features

RAG vs Knowledge Graph comparison
Employee relationship visualization
Performance insights & charts

🧠 Learning
RAG retrieves information.
Knowledge Graph connects and understands employee growth.

this project shows how structured knowledge can improve decision-making in employee
